description:
In this challenge, I attempt to create a Ukulele tuner in JavaScript using p5.js, ml5.js and the pre-trained machine learning model CREPE: A Convolutional Representation for Pitch Estimation. I challenge you to make one with a more elegant and creative interface!

💻 Code: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/151-ukulele-tuner.html
